Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.45,0:00:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪索 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.62,0:00:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.33,0:00:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,呵…呼…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.46,0:00:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.06,0:00:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,惡化地這麼快的嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.01,0:00:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,查克羅 你們要加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.43,0:00:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多大家都到極限了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.36,0:01:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 大叔 會被盯上的！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.66,0:01:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪索 太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.54,0:01:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,庫奇巴！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.97,0:01:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那個人生的偉大死的光榮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.06,0:01:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,為了我們島上群眾的幸福生活
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.23,0:01:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,她犧牲自己 一生毫不利己專門利人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.20,0:02:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你們懂得她生命的價值嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.62,0:02:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼能被你們這種人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.29,0:02:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼能被你們這種人奪去她的性命！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.07,0:02:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你在搞什麼飛機 你這混蛋白痴豆芽菜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.12,0:02:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋白痴豆芽菜…？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.84,0:02:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,別 別來礙事！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.81,0:02:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你想白白尋死嗎 大叔！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.88,0:02:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,別廢話！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.78,0:02:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,這才不是廢話！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.99,0:02:38.93,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1106,995)}thymia
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.99,0:02:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你又不能發動情念力！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.08,0:02:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你說什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.45,0:02:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,真難看…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.82,0:02:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,真難看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.29,0:02:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,留有感情的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.75,0:02:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,總是活在憎恨與憤怒之中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.79,0:02:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,真是難看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.15,0:02:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,難看或許是我們的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.51,0:02:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.40,0:03:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,可沒道理被你們這些蒙面殺人狂說！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.47,0:03:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,小孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.93,0:03:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.68,0:03:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,下不了手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.99,0:03:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我會去報台霞姐姐的仇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.01,0:03:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,夠了…不用了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.09,0:03:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,…我女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.40,0:03:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,要是還活著的話 會變成什麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:03:59.97,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,995)}παγώνι
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:03:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,帕格尼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.00,0:04:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,歐尼！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.76,0:04:23.61,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(846,995)}φάλαινα
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.76,0:04:23.61,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1044,995)}δαίμονας
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.76,0:04:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,法萊那的惡靈…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.01,0:04:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,到底還是迷信 真無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.97,0:04:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,給我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.64,0:04:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,比沙海裡的微塵還要低劣的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.15,0:04:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不如就此消失！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.27,0:04:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,早就知道了！這種事情！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,被關在狹小的島上…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.69,0:04:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,對世界一無所知！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.47,0:04:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼都影響不了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.71,0:04:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是我們啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.74,0:04:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那種泥巴船早就不想待了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,所以！別來礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.74,0:04:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你這禿子！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,歐尼！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.80,0:05:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你們這群傢伙不過是螳臂擋車！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.03,0:05:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我們是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,「體內鼴鼠」！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.44,0:05:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,都給我上！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.19,0:05:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我跟歐尼在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.95,0:06:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,就總是最強的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.61,0:06:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,再可別看扁咱們了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,歐尼！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧 歐…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.96,0:06:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,捉隻老鼠還這麼磨磨唧唧的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.75,0:06:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,給我馬上幹掉他們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.72,0:06:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我…們…總在…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.29,0:06:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,一起的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,歐…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.29,0:06:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,尼比…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.68,0:07:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我來帶你到外面的世界去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:14.24,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1046,995)}thymia
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,居然能用情念力！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.69,0:07:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會…這不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.98,0:07:26.52,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,995)}νοῦς
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.98,0:07:26.52,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1084,995)}αὔρα
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.98,0:07:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,「魂形之間」裡 念紋怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,歐尼！ 尼比！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.66,0:07:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,查克羅 危險！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:44.85,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(928,995)}δαίμονας
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,惡靈…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.95,0:08:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,黎可斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.90,0:08:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,查克羅！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.50,0:08:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,這…這種事 怎麼可能發生…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.77,0:08:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,對了！ 就是因為觸犯了禁忌！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:38.61,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(900,995)}όρκα
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,都怪奧爾卡的昏招！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:42.94,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(692,995)}δαίμονας
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,讓惡靈覺醒了…！ 都怪他…！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.52,0:08:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,哇…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.15,0:08:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.70,0:09:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 蓬蓬頭！ 這是怎麼回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.67,0:09:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎麼知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.39,0:09:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,查奇…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.93,0:09:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,黎可斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.46,0:09:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,黎可斯！ 你沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.12,0:09:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,歐尼！ 歐尼！ 你在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.60,0:10:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,尼比…！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.08,0:10:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,本來是我一直想要你不要丟下我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.50,0:10:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到 居然倒過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.42,0:10:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,尼比…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.38,0:10:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思… 這是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.91,0:10:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不能讓你搭上這條船
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,布奇…艾吉洛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.65,0:10:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.94,0:10:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.37,0:11:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.62,0:11:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,多不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.24,0:11:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我還是第一次見歐尼你哭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.99,0:11:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,尼比…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.48,0:11:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,尼比…！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.52,0:12:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,對了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.48,0:12:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,歐尼你或許覺得 要是不能從泥鯨出去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.41,0:12:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我們就沒有意義了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.95,0:12:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我…其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.50,0:12:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,比你以為的還要…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.39,0:12:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,可以說是滿足於現狀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.85,0:12:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,一面憧憬著外面的世界 一面在那座島上…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.71,0:13:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,每天跟你一起眺望不變的藍天與大海
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.66,0:13:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,僅僅如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.29,0:13:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,就最好不過了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.80,0:13:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不對…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.59,0:13:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有意義的…是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.08,0:13:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,要不是跟你們相見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.27,0:13:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,要不是跟你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.42,0:13:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,連我活在這裡的理由都不存在！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.12,0:13:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,歐尼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.99,0:13:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我會一直等著你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.51,0:14:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我見識見識
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.88,0:14:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,拂卻沙塵 這個世界的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,尼比…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.85,0:14:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,尼比！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.76,0:14:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,尼比！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.00,0:15:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,歐尼！
